  "text": "where \u03c0 h is an operator defined such that (\u03c0 hzi,h \u2212z i,h ) approximates the interpolation error as in [CITATION_1] , typically defined by local averaging, to define the estimators \u03b7 k , \u03be k , \u03b6 k according to the rule",
